DTSTAMP:20260319T143634Z
DTSTART:20260325T194500
DTEND:20260325T220000
SUMMARY:18+ Figure Drawing: March Session
LOCATION:Unkindness Art\, 2923 North Avenue\, Richmond\, VA 23222
DESCRIPTION:Ongoing nude figure drawing series open to all artists 18+. March session features a long pose with a single model. Tickets required in advance. 18+ ID required at door. No phones or photos during event.\\n\\nCost: $10\\n\\nRegister: https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/nude-figure-drawing-march-2026
URL:https://www.unkindnessart.com/events/nude-figure-drawing-march-2026
END:VEVENT
